  "texts": [
    "\"-Student 5",
    "As demonstrated earlier, every student who experimented with AI tools in their entrepreneurship module discovered that AI was user-friendly, especially with the appropriate prompts.",
    "They also found that generative AI, such as ChatGPT improved their learning experience by streamlining tasks and quickly accessing the necessary information.",
    "Our study suggests four benefits of the usage of AI tools from students' perspective, namely increased productivity, personalised learning, idea generation and improved linguistic capabilities.",
    "All students using AI tools reported that could increase their productivity."
